Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:47.86,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\fsp10\1c&H43E5FF&\3c&H0200CF&\4c&H43E5FF&\shad1\frz16\pos(185,188)}NcDonalds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:47.86,Background,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san quit the Kyuseikai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not an Insei anymore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, even those that graduate\Nusually stay until March.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyuseikai is the Go school that Isumi-san\Nalways studied at, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Isumi-san's going to do now that\Nhe's quit the Kyuseikai and the Insei program.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya, do you know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I couldn't bring myself to call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I went to take a look during\Nan Insei study session.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And Shinoda-sensei told me that Isumi-san quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What... What did he say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That this may be better for Isumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:36.31,Memory,,0,0,0,,Here. It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:37.72,Memory,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.40,Memory,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:51.03,Memory,,0,0,0,,He's probably trying to look at himself\Nfrom a different perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.66,Memory,,0,0,0,,Even though he has quit the Kyuseikai\Nand the Insei program,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:04:00.68,Memory,,0,0,0,,playing games isn't the only\Nway to get better at Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:06.35,Memory,,0,0,0,,At his level, it's more than enough\Nto replay other games.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:11.03,Memory,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's important to be alone for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How can the teacher say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san might have given up on becoming a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:27.76,Background,,0,0,0,,The teacher said 'Isumi-kun still hasn't\Ngiven up, he'll come back next year'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He looked serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,'He definitely doesn't think that\Nhis Go will end here.' He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.61,Memory,,0,0,0,,Let Isumi-kun worry about himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.56,Memory,,0,0,0,,You have yourself to worry about, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.33,Memory,,0,0,0,,You're a pro already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what he said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:53.34,Sai,,0,0,0,,You too, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyways...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd teach you how to record games today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Record games?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do it sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Though they don't usually ask people\Ngoing to school to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We record all pro matches after\Nthe third elimination round.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how to record a Kifu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to record the times, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:17.88,Background,,0,0,0,,Here's an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:24.20,Background,,0,0,0,,You record how long they spent\Non each move, or the total time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.96,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, you can't possibly do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's byou-yomi, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya, you can do this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How can Waya do something like this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You called me out over something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this as a favor for you! Remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:44.67,Background,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.20,Background,,0,0,0,,Don't mess up when you're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.10,Background,,0,0,0,,And? How are you supposed to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:50.66,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru is finally taking a step\Ninto the world of the pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyways, pros have to play\Ngames, right?! Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When do I get to play Touya!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know, Waya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:05:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be playing lots of people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you, or Saeki-san, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I going to play Touya-Meijin, too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.29,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:12.81,Sai,,0,0,0,,Will I be playing him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be at least five years\Nbefore you play the top pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I keep winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't play them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:23.25,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes, can we!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you keep winning you\Nwill reach the top, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The second elimination round is as far\Nas pros lower than 4-dan can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To Touya, and to Touya's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.22,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same world already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be playing them someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:47.80,Sai,,0,0,0,,'I'...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play Murakami 2-dan from\Nthe Wakajishisen again, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to play Ogata 9-dan or\Nthat old guy who's Honinbou, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be elated!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:01.44,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to play Touya first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play against Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:07.41,Sai,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still a lower-dan player.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you're lucky, you'll get\Nto play him sometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Our pairings are randomly made.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Random?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:17.56,Sai,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get to play Shirakawa-sensei or\NMorishita-sensei in a real match, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I keep saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't play high-dan players for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But we are connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we'll be playing sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we're in the same world already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:38.06,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.23,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one that's connected...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.12,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:46.23,Sai,,0,0,0,,It's just Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:49.55,Sai,,0,0,0,,Will Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.71,Sai,,0,0,0,,not let me play anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,375)}That is true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,375)}Right!? Let's see who becomes 2-dan first!
