Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.64,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Ten minutes before the match starts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Master Zama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, I still\Nhaven't congratulated you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sixth successful defense of the Meijin title.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Master Touya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:58.39,Background,,0,0,0,,But you lost the challenger rights to the Kisei title.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's because you're exhausted from\Nplaying too many matches, Master Touya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have lost the final match\Nto decide the challenger
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for the Kisei title, because I was tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am in the best condition today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it is your son who\Nis in the best of conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he undefeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He has had twenty straight wins so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The only match Akira lost was the new first dan\Nseries match, from right before he became pro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Zama,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,just that match against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll be trying to get revenge\Nfor your beloved little boy today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You first, Zama Ouza.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.24,NoteTimes,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad0\pos(277,62)}O\Nu\Nz\Na\N\NT\Ni\Nt\Nl\Ne\N\NM\Na\Nt\Nc\Nh
